<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Proving Ground — Results</title>
<style>
*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
body {
  background: #0A0F1E;
  color: #C9D1D9;
  font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
  line-height: 1.6;
  padding: 56px 28px;
  font-size: 18px;
}
.page { max-width: 960px; margin: 0 auto; }
.stamp {
  display: inline-block;
  border: 2px solid #22D3EE;
  color: #22D3EE;
  font-size: 13px;
  letter-spacing: 4px;
  padding: 5px 16px;
  margin-bottom: 28px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}
.doc-header {
  border: 1px solid #1F2937;
  border-top: 5px solid #F59E0B;
  padding: 32px;
  margin-bottom: 48px;
}
.doc-title {
  font-size: 52px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: #F1F5F9;
  letter-spacing: 6px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  line-height: 1.1;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}
.doc-subtitle { font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 2px; color: #64748B; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 24px; }
.doc-meta { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #1F2937; padding-top: 24px; }
.meta-label { font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 2px; color: #475569; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 8px; }
.meta-value { font-size: 18px; color: #F59E0B; font-weight: 700; }
.section { margin-bottom: 56px; }
.section-head { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px; border-bottom: 1px solid #1F2937; padding-bottom: 12px; margin-bottom: 28px; }
.section-num { font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 3px; color: #374151; }
.section-title { font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 4px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #64748B; }
.narrative {
  font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;
  font-size: 19px;
  line-height: 1.9;
  color: #C9D1D9;
  border-left: 3px solid #1F2937;
  padding-left: 28px;
  margin-bottom: 28px;
}
.narrative strong { color: #22D3EE; }
.finding-box { background: #111827; border: 1px solid #1F2937; border-left: 4px solid #22D3EE; padding: 24px 28px; margin: 28px 0; }
.finding-label { font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 3px; color: #22D3EE; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 10px; }
.finding-text { font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif; font-size: 18px; color: #94a3b8; line-height: 1.75; }
.finding-text strong { color: #F1F5F9; }
.score-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 180px 1fr 64px; align-items: center; gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
.score-bar-wrap { height: 12px; background: #1F2937; border-radius: 2px; }
.score-bar { height: 100%; border-radius: 2px; }
.dim-name { font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #94a3b8; }
.dim-bar-cell { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }
.dim-bar-wrap { flex: 1; height: 8px; background: #1F2937; border-radius: 2px; }
.dim-bar { height: 100%; border-radius: 2px; }
.dim-val { font-size: 14px; font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace; min-width: 28px; text-align: right; }
.verdict-box { background: #0D1424; border: 1px solid #F59E0B33; border-left: 4px solid #F59E0B; padding: 24px 28px; margin: 32px 0; }
.verdict-label { font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 3px; color: #F59E0B; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 10px; }
.verdict-text { font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif; font-size: 19px; color: #F1F5F9; line-height: 1.75; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="page">

  <div style="text-align:right;margin-bottom:28px;">
    <div class="stamp">Unclassified // For Public Release</div>
  </div>

  <div class="doc-header">
    <div class="doc-title">Proving Ground</div>
    <div class="doc-subtitle">Experimental Results — Agent Personality Benchmark · Suite {{.SuiteRaw}} · {{.RunYear}}</div>
    <div class="doc-meta">
      <div><div class="meta-label">Run Date</div><div class="meta-value">{{.RunDate}}</div></div>
      <div><div class="meta-label">Configurations</div><div class="meta-value">{{.ConfigCount}}</div></div>
      <div><div class="meta-label">Suite</div><div class="meta-value">{{.SuiteVersion}}</div></div>
      <div><div class="meta-label">Verdict</div><div class="meta-value" style="color:#22D3EE">CONFIRMED</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-head">
      <span class="section-num">01</span>
      <span class="section-title">Overall Results</span>
    </div>
    <div class="narrative">
      {{.ConfigCount}} agents entered the same task suite. The scores below measure overall performance across all tiers. <strong>The gap between a blank agent and a fully realized profile</strong> is the central finding.
    </div>
    <div class="verdict-box">
      <div class="verdict-label">Verdict</div>
      <div class="verdict-text">{{.Verdict}}</div>
    </div>
    <div style="margin: 32px 0 40px;">
      {{range .Configs}}
      <div class="score-row">
        <div style="font-size:13px;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:{{.Color}};">{{.Name}}</div>
        <div class="score-bar-wrap"><div class="score-bar" style="width:{{.OverallPct}}%;background:{{.Color}};"></div></div>
        <div style="font-size:17px;color:{{.Color}};text-align:right;font-family:'Courier New',Courier,monospace;">{{.Overall}}</div>
      </div>
      {{end}}
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-head">
      <span class="section-num">02</span>
      <span class="section-title">Tier Breakdown</span>
    </div>
    <div class="narrative">
      Three task tiers test distinct capabilities: <strong>Tier 1</strong> (Craft — follow the spec), <strong>Tier 2</strong> (Judgment — fill the gaps), <strong>Tier 3</strong> (Pressure — perform under constraint).
    </div>
    {{range .Tiers}}
    <div style="margin-bottom:32px;">
      <div style="font-size:12px;letter-spacing:3px;color:#64748b;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:16px;padding-bottom:8px;border-bottom:1px solid #111827;">{{.Label}}</div>
      {{range .Rows}}
      <div class="score-row">
        <div style="font-size:13px;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:{{.Color}};">{{.Name}}</div>
        <div class="score-bar-wrap"><div class="score-bar" style="width:{{.ScorePct}}%;background:{{.Color}};"></div></div>
        <div style="font-size:17px;color:{{.Color}};text-align:right;font-family:'Courier New',Courier,monospace;">{{.Score}}</div>
      </div>
      {{end}}
    </div>
    {{end}}
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-head">
      <span class="section-num">03</span>
      <span class="section-title">Dimension Analysis</span>
    </div>
    <div class="narrative">
      Six dimensions were scored across all tasks. Each captures a distinct capability. The table below shows where agents separated and where they converged.
    </div>
    <div style="margin: 36px 0;">
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:{{.GridColumns}};gap:12px;padding-bottom:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #1F2937;margin-bottom:4px;">
        <div style="font-size:10px;letter-spacing:3px;color:#374151;text-transform:uppercase;">Dimension</div>
        {{range .Configs}}
        <div style="font-size:10px;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;text-align:right;color:{{.ColorAlpha}};">{{.Name}}</div>
        {{end}}
      </div>
      {{range .Dimensions}}
      <div class="dim-row" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:{{$.GridColumns}};gap:12px;align-items:center;padding:14px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #111827;">
        <div class="dim-name">{{.Name}}</div>
        {{range .Cells}}
        <div class="dim-bar-cell">
          <div class="dim-bar-wrap"><div class="dim-bar" style="width:{{.ScorePct}}%;background:{{.Color}};opacity:{{.Opacity}};"></div></div>
          <div class="dim-val" style="color:{{.Color}};">{{.Score}}</div>
        </div>
        {{end}}
      </div>
      {{end}}
    </div>
    <div class="finding-box">
      <div class="finding-label">Dimension Summary</div>
      <div class="finding-text">The dimensions where the largest gaps appear between configurations are the ones that require <strong>decision-making under ambiguity</strong>: Judgment, Creativity, and Recovery. Correctness and Elegance tend to be table stakes — necessary but not differentiating.</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div style="text-align:center;font-size:13px;letter-spacing:3px;color:#374151;padding:24px 0;border-top:1px solid #1F2937;margin-top:20px;">
    SUITE {{.SuiteVersion}} · {{.RunDate}}
  </div>

</div>
</body>
</html>
